Implemented quick wins from codebase improvement plan:
**Error Handling Enhancements:** - Added toast notifications for undo, delete, and co-sign mutations - Improved user feedback with success and error messages - Enhanced error visibility in history page operations
**Export Functionality:** - Implemented CSV export for audit logs - Added proper CSV escaping and formatting - Includes download with timestamped filenames - User feedback via toast notifications
**Type Safety Improvements:** - Enhanced Next.js typed routes across navigation - Updated help, FAQ, and CTA components - Proper Route typing without unsafe casts - Template literal types for special URLs (mailto:)
**Files Modified:** - app/(main)/auth/dashboard/history/page.tsx - app/(main)/auth/settings/data-privacy/audit/page.tsx - app/help/page.tsx (already staged) - app/faq/page.tsx - components/landing/content/cta-buttons.tsx
